data.description: Welcome to your new home in Southton Village, a community that seamlessly blends modern living with amenities. This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath residence, spanning 2239 sqft, is perfectly situated on a corner lot, providing both privacy and easy access to the community's walking trails and park located next door to the home. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully upgraded home with an oversized covered back patio, ideal for entertaining or enjoying quiet evenings. The large storage shed offers practical convenience for all your storage needs. The heart of the home, the kitchen, features oversized cabinets, providing ample storage and a stylish touch.    Upstairs, the owner's suite is a retreat with a soaking tub, double vanity, and a serene atmosphere. All bedrooms are conveniently located on the upper level, ensuring a cohesive and private living space.    Southton Village offers residents a lifestyle of luxury and convenience. Take leisurely strolls along scenic walking trails, or take advantage of the exciting playground right next door. Just minutes from downtown San Antonio, this community is served by quality schools like Highland Forest Elementary, Legacy Middle School, and East Central High School, all part of the East Central Independent School District.    Immerse yourself in the rich culture and entertainment options nearby, including the San Antonio Missions Historical Park, SeaWorld, Six Flags Fiesta Texas, and the iconic Riverwalk. Make this charming corner-lot home your gateway to an elevated living experience in a vibrant community.    Exclusions: Curtains and curtain rods.
